28
{
  name { Top of the Tower  }
  desc {
"   A pennant, ragged, worn, and bleached almost white, flutters fitfully in
the wind.  To the north, all along the horizon you see an ocean of
mountains.  The peaks with their white tops give the impression of a sea
storm frozen in place, preserved for all the ages.  The clouds moving above
this range of mountains are met by darker columns of smoke that rise from
the tops of some mountains far to the northeast.
  }
  sector { City }
  flags { no_sum, private }
  exits {
	to { d, 27 }
  }
}
